in foul ball country.

19:36.865 --> 19:40.045
Come on.
The Robin stuff was completely true.

19:41.332 --> 19:42.552
Damn it, Barney.

19:42.672 --> 19:44.784
I mean, for the last time,

19:44.904 --> 19:46.914
you can't... you can't

19:47.162 --> 19:49.214
be in love with Robin
and still be sleeping

19:49.334 --> 19:51.203
with every bimbo on the planet.

19:51.436 --> 19:52.990
