20:18.244 --> 20:19.882
Oh, I'm not confused.

20:20.622 --> 20:22.174
You know who is confused?

20:22.676 --> 20:23.675
Bimbos.

20:24.037 --> 20:26.768
They're easily confused.
It's one of the thousand little things

20:26.887 --> 20:28.251
I love about them.

20:28.610 --> 20:30.555
I love their vacant,

20:30.771 --> 20:34.527
trusting stares, their sluggish,
unencumbered minds,

20:35.121 --> 20:37.013
their unresolved daddy issues.

20:37.720 --> 20:40.005
I love them and they love me.

20:40.821 --> 20:44.478
Bimbos have always been there for me,
through thick and thin.

20:45.158 --> 20:47.313
Mostly thin.
B- man don't do thick crust.

